content.question: For time <math alttext="t greater than or equal to 0" display="inline" overflow="scroll"><mstyle><mrow><mi>t</mi><mo>≥</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></mstyle></math>, the position of a particle moving in the <math alttext="x y" display="inline" overflow="scroll"><mstyle><mrow><mi>x</mi><mi>y</mi></mrow></mstyle></math>-plane is given by the vector-valued function <math alttext="f" display="inline" overflow="scroll"><mstyle><mrow><mi>f</mi></mrow></mstyle></math>. If the velocity of the particle is given by <math alttext="v of t, equals, open angled bracket, 6 times t squared, minus, 5 times t to the fourth power, comma, 12 times t cubed, plus 6, close angled bracket" display="inline" overflow="scroll"><mstyle><mrow><mi>v</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi>t</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mo>⟨</mo><mrow><mn>6</mn><msup><mrow><mi>t</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup><mo>−</mo><mn>5</mn><msup><mrow><mi>t</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>4</mn></mrow></msup><mo>,</mo><mn>12</mn><msup><mrow><mi>t</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>3</mn></mrow></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>6</mn></mrow><mo>⟩</mo></mrow></mstyle></math>, which of the following could be an expression for <math alttext="f of t" display="inline" overflow="scroll"><mstyle><mrow><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi>t</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow></mrow></mstyle></math> ?

choices.label: <math alttext="open angled bracket, 12 t, minus, 20 times t cubed, comma, 36 times t squared, close angled bracket" display="inline" overflow="scroll"><mstyle><mrow><mrow><mrow><mo>⟨</mo><mrow><mn>12</mn><mi>t</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>20</mn><msup><mrow><mi>t</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>3</mn></mrow></msup><mo>,</mo><mn>36</mn><msup><mrow><mi>t</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup></mrow><mo>⟩</mo></mrow></mrow></mrow></mstyle></math>

<math alttext="open angled bracket, 6 times t squared, minus, 5 times t to the fourth power, comma, 3 times t to the fourth power, plus 6, t, plus 7, close angled bracket" display="inline" overflow="scroll"><mstyle><mrow><mrow><mrow><mo>⟨</mo><mrow><mn>6</mn><msup><mrow><mi>t</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup><mo>−</mo><mn>5</mn><msup><mrow><mi>t</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>4</mn></mrow></msup><mo>,</mo><mn>3</mn><msup><mrow><mi>t</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>4</mn></mrow></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>6</mn><mi>t</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>7</mn></mrow><mo>⟩</mo></mrow></mrow></mrow></mstyle></math>

<math alttext="open angled bracket, 2 times t cubed, minus, t to the fifth power, plus 5, comma, 12 times t cubed, plus 6, close angled bracket" display="inline" overflow="scroll"><mstyle><mrow><mrow><mrow><mo>⟨</mo><mrow><mn>2</mn><msup><mrow><mi>t</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>3</mn></mrow></msup><mo>−</mo><msup><mrow><mi>t</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>5</mn></mrow></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>12</mn><msup><mrow><mi>t</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>3</mn></mrow></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>6</mn></mrow><mo>⟩</mo></mrow></mrow></mrow></mstyle></math>

<math alttext="open angled bracket, 2 times t cubed, minus, t to the fifth power, minus 3, comma, 3 times t to the fourth power, plus 6, t, plus 4, close angled bracket" display="inline" overflow="scroll"><mstyle><mrow><mrow><mrow><mo>⟨</mo><mrow><mn>2</mn><msup><mrow><mi>t</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>3</mn></mrow></msup><mo>−</mo><msup><mrow><mi>t</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>5</mn></mrow></msup><mo>−</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>3</mn><msup><mrow><mi>t</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>4</mn></mrow></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>6</mn><mi>t</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>4</mn></mrow><mo>⟩</mo></mrow></mrow></mrow></mstyle></math>
